plot: On Celina's last day as a rookie, John gives her one final test, Bailey makes a new friend, and Lucy places her faith in Seth for an undercover assignment.

Bailey's not talking to Nolan. They respond to a call at a woman's shelter and Bailey bonds with the victim and talks to her about her issues. Tamara calls Lucy to tell her that someone in her school is selling drugs. They need to send someone undercover. And Lucy reluctantly decides to let Seth who's back to do it. He and Tamara spend time together which worries Lucy. Nolan and Suarez get their shop get stolen when they pull over a van that they think is suspicious and the two men in the van overpower them. They discover they sell guns. They track them down and arrest them. It's Suarez's last day as a rookie.Harper needs to decide if she wants to support James' crusade against the LAPD.—Rcs0411@yahoo.com
